In a large bowl combine tomatoes, bell pepper, garlic, mozzarella, olives, oil, vinegar, and salt and pepper to taste and let sauce stand 30 minutes. While sauce is standing, in a 6-quart kettle bring 5 quarts salted water to a boil. Add pasta and cook until_al dente_. Drain pasta well and transfer to bowl containing sauce. Add herbs and toss well.